    show GTS unique-2
    GTS "But as the saying goes, easy come, easy go. The nori was quite satisfying regardless."
    show GTS neutral
    MC "I..."
    MC "You..."
    MC "I'm sorry, you lost {i}how{/i} much? And you're just... {i}okay{/i} with it?"
